### Phase 5 — Job View Tracking

#### [MODIFY] jobs/entities/job.entity.ts
```ts
@Column({ name: 'view_count', type: 'int', default: 0 })
viewCount: number;
```

#### [NEW] migration: add `view_count` column

#### [MODIFY] public-jobs.service.ts — `getJobDetail(jobId, userId?)`:
- Increment `view_count` atomic: `UPDATE job SET view_count = view_count + 1 WHERE id = :id`
- Nếu user là candidate, có thể skip nếu đã xem trong session (tùy chọn)

