### Phase 6 — Email Notifications

#### [NEW] src/mail/mail.module.ts
```ts
// Sử dụng @nestjs-modules/mailer + Nodemailer + Handlebars templates
MailerModule.forRootAsync({
  useFactory: (configService) => ({
    transport: { host, port, auth },
    defaults: { from: '"ATS System" <no-reply@ats.com>' },
    template: { dir: './src/mail/templates', adapter: new HandlebarsAdapter() }
  })
})
```

#### [NEW] src/mail/mail.service.ts
- `sendWelcomeEmail(user)` 
- `sendPasswordResetEmail(email, resetLink)`
- `sendApplicationStatusEmail(candidate, job, newStatus)`
- `sendJobInvitationEmail(candidate, job, employer)`

#### [NEW] src/mail/templates/ — Handlebars templates (.hbs)
- `welcome.hbs`
- `reset-password.hbs`
- `application-status.hbs`
- `job-invitation.hbs`

#### [MODIFY] auth.service.ts — gọi mail service trong `forgotPassword()`
#### [MODIFY] employer-applications.service.ts — gọi mail service khi `updateApplicationStatus()`
#### [MODIFY] employer-headhunting.service.ts — gọi mail service khi `sendJobInvitation()`

